  <h1>Classic Pancakes</h1>

  <p>
    These classic pancakes are fluffy, easy to make, and perfect for a quick breakfast or brunch.
  </p>

  <h2>Ingredients</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>1 cup all-purpose flour</li>
    <li>1 tablespoon sugar</li>
    <li>1 teaspoon baking powder</li>
    <li>1 cup milk</li>
    <li>1 egg</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Instructions</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>Mix the flour, sugar, and baking powder in a bowl.</li>
    <li>Add the milk and egg, then whisk until smooth.</li>
    <li>Heat a pan over medium heat and lightly grease it.</li>
    <li>Pour batter into the pan and cook until bubbles form, then flip.</li>
    <li>Cook until golden brown and serve warm.</li>
  </ol>

